Zone: PoS - assemble in Toxx spires<br>
Time: 930 PM EST to about 1AM<br>
<br>
Attendees - 18 - 24. exactly 24 highest levels will get priority if I cut people. 2 chanters is bonus 3 is Perf - while we wait for koS to Spawn on Isle 4 about 2 1/2 hours after raid starts <br>
<br>
channel: Skyraid<br>
Goal. necro drop from KoS on Isle 4, get to Isle 7 for mage hat.<br>
<br>
Preferance: Would like 3(4) plate class tanks3 clerics, 2 chanters, 1 (2) monk and minimum of one Wizard.<br>
<br>
Friday we plowing to KoS - dropping him.. and porting to Isle 1 and dueling - leaving corpses with a bag with just your keys in them.  Sat we will bring everyone back up that can come - and going back to kos - droping him and then moving to Spiroc/bazzat / drake Isles.  So long as we get at least 12 of the same people from day one - we are a go for summoning up the rest of the players to Isle 4 with kill the player/rez/summon re rez technique.  shouldn't be a problem.<br>
